<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ur" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>چالان - اکاؤنٹس</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Nastaliq+Urdu:wght@400;700&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Nastaliq Urdu', serif;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2c5aa0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header h2 {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .challan-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .challan-info h3 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #495057;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #212529;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .payment-details {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .payment-details h3 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .breakdown-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .breakdown-table th,
        .breakdown-table td {
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .breakdown-table th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .breakdown-table .amount {
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .total-section {
            background: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            border-top: 2px solid #2c5aa0;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .payment-instructions {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .payment-instructions h4 {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .payment-instructions ul {
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        
        .payment-instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding-top: 10px;
            min-width: 150px;
        }
        
        .signature-box h4 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .signature-box p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .qr-code {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .urgent {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body {
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .header, .challan-info, .payment-details, .footer {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>محکمہ ہاؤسنگ</h1>
        <h2>چالان - اکاؤنٹس</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="challan-info">
        <h3>چالان کی تفصیلات</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">چالان نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{accountsBreakdown.id}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">تاریخ:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{formatDate accountsBreakdown.createdAt}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">درخواست نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{application.id}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">ادائیگی کی تاریخ:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{formatDate accountsBreakdown.paymentDueDate}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="payment-details">
        <h3>ادائیگی کی تفصیلات</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">درخواست کنندہ:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{application.applicantName}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">پلاٹ نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.plotNumber}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">بلاک:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.block}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">سکشن:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.section}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <table class="breakdown-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>تفصیل</th>
                    <th>رقم (روپے)</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.transferFee}}
                <tr>
                    <td>منتقلی فیس</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.transferFee}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.stampDuty}}
                <tr>
                    <td>سٹامپ ڈیوٹی</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.stampDuty}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.registrationFee}}
                <tr>
                    <td>رجسٹریشن فیس</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.registrationFee}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.mutationFee}}
                <tr>
                    <td>میوٹیشن فیس</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.mutationFee}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.otherCharges}}
                <tr>
                    <td>دیگر چارجز</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.otherCharges}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if accountsBreakdown.lateFee}}
                <tr>
                    <td>لیٹ فیس</td>
                    <td class="amount">{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.lateFee}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <div class="total-section">
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>کل رقم:</span>
                <span>{{formatCurrency accountsBreakdown.totalAmount}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        {{#if accountsBreakdown.paymentDueDate}}
        <div class="urgent">
            <strong>ادائیگی کی آخری تاریخ: {{formatDate accountsBreakdown.paymentDueDate}}</strong>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        <div class="payment-instructions">
            <h4>ادائیگی کی ہدایات</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>ادائیگی بینک ڈرافٹ یا چیک کے ذریعے کی جائے</li>
                <li>چیک/ڈرافٹ "محکمہ ہاؤسنگ" کے نام پر ہو</li>
                <li>ادائیگی کی تصدیق کے لیے اصل رسید پیش کریں</li>
                <li>لیٹ فیس سے بچنے کے لیے وقت پر ادائیگی کریں</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <h4>اکاؤنٹس افسر</h4>
            <p>دستخط</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <h4>تاریخ</h4>
            <p>{{formatDate accountsBreakdown.createdAt}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>یہ چالان اکاؤنٹس شعبے کی جانب سے جاری کیا گیا ہے</p>
        <p>درخواست نمبر: {{application.id}} | چالان نمبر: {{accountsBreakdown.id}}</p>
        <div class="qr-code">
            {{#if qrCodeDataURL}}
            <img src="{{qrCodeDataURL}}" alt="QR Code" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;">
            {{else}}
            QR Code<br>
            {{application.id}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
